description: Coach Matt Wellington wants to show Damien Stone that he appreciates the hustle he's been bringing to the field. But, when sandy blonde hunk Matt finds a big dildo in his star player's bag he worries that Damien has forgotten his top athletes only policy. Matt makes the sculpted dark-haired Damien pound his ass to prove that he's still the top that he needs to be to stay on the team.
title: Top Of Your Game
